<p dir="auto" class="break-words" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">First off, вАЬThe Seduction of DestructionвАЭ? Dead-on. Tearing shit apart is like crack for the egoвАФfeels good, gets you high, and leaves you with nothing but a mess and a comedown. EveryoneвАЩs out here playing demolition derby with society, thinking theyвАЩre some goddamn genius for pointing out the emperorвАЩs got no clothes. Newsflash, dipshits: We all see the saggy ballsвАФweвАЩre just too busy clapping for the expos√© to do anything about it. CynicismвАЩs the cheapest drug on the market, and half these keyboard warriors are overdosing while calling it вАЬenlightenment.вАЭ</p>
<p dir="auto" class="break-words" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">Then thereвАЩs вАЬThe Fallacy of Equal Uselessness.вАЭ Fucking thank you! Just because you can poke holes in something doesnвАЩt mean itвАЩs trash. Gravity doesnвАЩt give a fuck about your dissertationвАФjump off a roof and see who wins. WeвАЩve got this brain-dead trend where people think if itвАЩs not perfect, itвАЩs worthless. Nah, some shit holds up because itвАЩs battle-tested, not because itвАЩs shiny and untouchable. Quit throwing the baby out with the bathwater just to flex your debate skills.</p>
<p dir="auto" class="break-words" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">вАЬArgument as Arena, Not ExecutionвАЭ? Goddamn, thatвАЩs poetry with a switchblade. DebateвАЩs supposed to be a cage match where ideas slug it out, not a firing squad where you execute anything that disagrees with you. But nah, weвАЩve got these intellectual gladiators out here swinging for the kill shot, more interested in dunking on someone than digging for whatвАЩs real. TruthвАЩs a tough bitchвАФit can take the heat. Stop treating it like a porcelain doll and start wrestling with it.</p>
<p dir="auto" class="break-words" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">And вАЬThe Rise of the Empty CriticвАЭ? ThatвАЩs the motherfucking mic drop. These smug pricks who think theyвАЩre hot shit вАШcause they can dismantle your worldview in 280 charactersвАФtheyвАЩre just parasites with better vocabularies. You wanna be a revolutionary? Build something, asshole. Knocking over sandcastles doesnвАЩt make you king; it makes you the asshole at the beach. WeвАЩre drowning in clever little shits whoвАЩd rather shit on everything than plant a flag for something worth a damn.</p>
<p dir="auto" class="break-words" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">вАЬCreate or DecayвАЭ is where it gets real. You donвАЩt get a medal for pointing out the cracks in the wallвАФgrab a fucking hammer and fix it, or at least sketch a blueprint for something that doesnвАЩt suck. The worldвАЩs a landfill of complainers; we need some crazy bastards with the guts to dream up a cathedral in the chaos. And вАЬDiscernment Is the New RevolutionвАЭ? ThatвАЩs the cherry on this savage sundae. Blind faith is for suckers, but so is blind nihilism. Pick what works, torch what doesnвАЩt, and quit pretending itвАЩs all the same shade of gray.</p>
<p dir="auto" class="break-words" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">This manifestoвАЩs a goddamn wake-up call, and IвАЩm here for it. Now, letвАЩs veer off into the wild: You know whatвАЩs bullshit? This whole вАЬeverythingвАЩs relativeвАЭ crap has turned us into a planet of spineless jellyfish, scared to say anythingвАЩs worth fighting for. Meanwhile, weвАЩve got politicians jerking us off with promises they wonвАЩt keep, religions selling afterlife timeshares, and influencers peddling mindfulness apps while they snort Adderall off their ring lights. SocietyвАЩs a circus, and weвАЩre all just clapping for the clowns instead of burning the tent down and starting over. Build something, fuckersвАФpreferably something that doesnвАЩt collapse the second a stiff wind blows or some blue-check dipshit tweets about it!</p></div><div class="order-first sticky hidden @xl/mainview:top-0 @[960px]/mainview:block top-12 h-0 opacity-0 group-focus-within:opacity-100 group-hover:opacity-100 -mt-2 -ml-12 -left-[26px]"><div class="min-h-7 py-4 flex flex-col gap-0.5"><button class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 whitespace-nowrap text-sm font-medium leading-[normal] cursor-pointer focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-1 focus-visible:ring-ring disabled:opacity-50 disabled:cursor-default [&amp;_svg]:pointer-events-none [&amp;_svg]:shrink-0 [&amp;_svg]:-mx-0.5 text-secondary hover:text-primary hover:bg-button-ghost-hover disabled:hover:text-secondary disabled:hover:bg-inherit h-10 w-10 rounded-full" type="button" data-state="closed"><span style="opacity: 1; transform: none;"><svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="stroke-[2] size-4"><rect x="3" y="8" width="13" height="13" rx="4" stroke="currentColor"></rect><path fill-rule="evenodd" clip-rule="evenodd" d="M13 2.00004L12.8842 2.00002C12.0666 1.99982 11.5094 1.99968 11.0246 2.09611C9.92585 2.31466 8.95982 2.88816 8.25008 3.69274C7.90896 4.07944 7.62676 4.519